Service of MTK bandwidth control module (BWC)


WHAT IT DOES?
=============

BWC(bandwidth controller) service provide binder interface to change the bus related 
configurtion in the runtime, which optimizes the bus access latency in multimedia 
scenarios. BWC is required for all MTK multimedia middleware implementation including
camera and video middlewares.


HOW IT WAS BUILT?
==================
It needs the following library from AOSP:
1.  liblog.so
2.  libcutils.so
3.  libbinder.so

HOW TO USE IT?
==============

Provide function-based interface for MTK multimedia middlewares
The interface is defined in bwc common headers. (vendor/mediatek/proprietary/hardware/bwc)

All the source code of this library were written by MediaTek co..
